you could and couldn't do,

38:12.652 --> 38:14.153
what you were capable of.

38:15.453 --> 38:16.822
Cause I had heard that

38:16.856 --> 38:20.393
you could be one of the most
deadly men in my employ with a gun.

38:20.425 --> 38:21.694
That your kill count
far exceeded

38:21.727 --> 38:23.696
any of the street thugs
I scrape out of the gutter

38:23.729 --> 38:25.097
whenever I need something done.

38:26.332 --> 38:28.200
I told you
that was just a rumor.

38:30.403 --> 38:32.338
Well, I think the rumor
was a rumor.

38:34.807 --> 38:35.975
I knew you were,

38:36.008 --> 38:38.411
and presumably still are
very capable.

38:40.012 --> 38:41.380
Yes, sir.

38:45.651 --> 38:46.752
So what are you saying, Kellin?

38:49.755 --> 38:52.091
Not only are you capable

38:52.124 --> 38:54.526
of doing what you previously
did not want to do...

39:00.032 --> 39:03.102
but now you're
willing and able

39:03.135 --> 39:06.439
