for something else?

39:27.793 --> 39:29.829
My schedule's opened up.

39:29.862 --> 39:33.199
I need work to fill it soon.

39:38.738 --> 39:40.239
How interesting.

39:42.074 --> 39:43.376
You see...

39:47.346 --> 39:50.816
