each other's problems.

40:10.136 --> 40:12.405
- Come on in.
- You hoo!

40:14.807 --> 40:16.541
Hey, listen, I've been thinking,

40:16.574 --> 40:19.045
and you don't need to make
any big plans here or anything

40:19.078 --> 40:21.847
'cause I've decided,
I'm ready to go.

40:21.881 --> 40:23.416
Hey, shut the fuck up, Dad.

40:23.449 --> 40:25.684
Okay. You kiss your mother
with that mouth?

40:25.718 --> 40:26.786
No.

40:26.819 --> 40:28.054
Well that's a good thing.

40:28.087 --> 40:29.688
You never know
what you're going to catch.

40:29.722 --> 40:31.791
All right, Dad.

40:31.824 --> 40:33.558
All right. I'm sorry.

40:33.591 --> 40:34.794
That's alright.

40:39.465 --> 40:40.533
How are you?

40:41.834 --> 40:43.536
It's a complicated conversation.

40:44.602 --> 40:46.038
- Yeah?
- Mm hmm.

40:46.072 --> 40:47.406
Taking your pain meds or what?

40:47.440 --> 40:49.675
Oh, God. They make me
so damn tired.

40:49.708 --> 40:52.645
I think it's better to just
stay awake with the pain,

40:52.678 --> 40:55.514
spend my last few days
clear-headed.

40:55.548 --> 40:59.118
Dad, enough of the
dramatic shit, okay?

40:59.151 --> 41:01.754
Please. You're not
going anywhere.

41:03.656 --> 41:04.790
What do you mean?

41:06.058 --> 41:07.393
I want to pay for treatment.

41:08.427 --> 41:10.262
Uh, how?

41:10.296 --> 41:12.198
They now start
paying personal drivers

41:12.231 --> 41:13.666
thousands of dollars
every night?

41:14.934 --> 41:17.203
I'll find a way. Okay?

41:17.236 --> 41:19.939
No, I don't want you to do that.

41:19.972 --> 41:22.074
No, Come on.
Even if they fix this,

41:22.108 --> 41:24.076
I don't have
that much time left anyway.

41:24.110 --> 41:25.610
So what's the point?

41:25.644 --> 41:27.746
It's just an extra day,
it'll pay double.

41:28.981 --> 41:31.517
Cut my own arm off.
You know that.

41:32.818 --> 41:34.353
I do know that.

41:35.287 --> 41:37.356
It's a damn good thing
nobody wants it.

41:42.795 --> 41:44.530
Now seriously,

41:44.563 --> 41:46.499
where would you get
that kind of money?

41:48.534 --> 41:54.006
Um, my boss, I told you
about, that lawyer.

41:54.039 --> 41:56.609
- Hmm.
- He's a bad guy.

41:58.410 --> 42:00.379
He's got these
foreign girls around.

42:01.247 --> 42:03.749
They're here illegally.

42:03.782 --> 42:06.919
Yeah, and normally, I just
I just drive for him.

42:08.120 --> 42:10.689
It's appointments,

42:10.723 --> 42:14.627
dinners with his dad's business
partners in hotel rooms.

42:14.660 --> 42:17.863
After, but I just,
I just drive.

42:20.266 --> 42:22.201
That pays what it pays.

42:22.234 --> 42:25.738
But I guess
there's this one girl

42:25.771 --> 42:27.239
who got into some trouble

42:28.807 --> 42:30.309
and he...

42:32.144 --> 42:34.513
he wants me to
drive her to Arizona

42:36.115 --> 42:39.385
and get rid of her.

42:40.953 --> 42:43.689
Get rid of her? Like?

42:43.722 --> 42:46.559
Like make it look like
a heroin overdose.

42:49.562 --> 42:52.331
You are, you are seriously
going to do this?

42:53.532 --> 42:54.867
Yes. Yes.

42:57.269 --> 42:58.604
What's wrong with you,
stop.

42:58.638 --> 43:00.739
- I can't even look at you right now.
- Dad, stop.

43:02.241 --> 43:04.109
- What's wrong with you?
- How dare you do this?

43:04.143 --> 43:05.411
What do you mean,
you're doing this for me?

43:05.444 --> 43:07.213
- You're not doing this for me.
- It's my decision.

43:07.246 --> 43:08.447
And I've made it okay?

43:08.480 --> 43:09.915
- I stand by it.
- No you're not.

43:09.949 --> 43:12.051
I look in those eyes right now
that looks so much like my own

43:12.084 --> 43:14.520
and you're telling me you're going
to do something like this for me?

43:14.553 --> 43:16.322
We have no choice.
We need the money.

43:16.355 --> 43:17.623
What am I going to do?
Just let you die?

43:17.657 --> 43:19.592
- I will not let that happen!
- No!

43:19.625 --> 43:22.261
You may think
you don't have a choice.

43:22.294 --> 43:23.462
We all have choices.

43:23.495 --> 43:25.431
- I've got a choice right now.
- No you don't.

43:25.464 --> 43:27.199
- Yes sir, I do.
- Dad, stop.

43:27.233 --> 43:29.435
Dad, stop! Dad!

43:29.468 --> 43:31.003
Dad!

43:36.475 --> 43:40.512
Seriously, where would you
get that kind of money?

43:43.515 --> 43:44.950
Well, I talked to my boss today.

43:46.218 --> 43:48.187
He's going to lend me
some money.

43:48.220 --> 43:50.690
Yeah, I mean, I'm gonna have to
work it off, of course, but

43:51.457 --> 43:53.025
yeah, he said he's gonna do it.

43:53.058 --> 43:55.361
So, it's good.

43:55.394 --> 43:57.796
He's going to lend you
that much money?

43:57.830 --> 43:59.265
I mean, I know
he's a lawyer, but...

43:59.298 --> 44:01.166
No, no. Yeah. No, he's got
the money to spare.

44:02.935 --> 44:04.671
What do you have to do for it?

44:05.571 --> 44:07.641
- Nothing dangerous?
- No, no, Dad.

44:07.674 --> 44:10.677
I'm just driving
this girl to Arizona

44:10.710 --> 44:12.845
for some house
he set up for her.

44:12.878 --> 44:14.313
Super simple.

44:14.346 --> 44:15.614
Who's the girl?

44:16.148 --> 44:17.816
You know her?

44:17.850 --> 44:19.418
No, no, no I don't.

44:19.451 --> 44:21.787
