if you eat at a fucking Arby's.

45:12.772 --> 45:13.906
Okay?

45:13.939 --> 45:15.474
I wish you had Nando's.

45:15.507 --> 45:19.211
Oh, God! I miss Nando's.

45:19.244 --> 45:20.979
What the hell's that?

45:21.013 --> 45:24.583
