45:28.954 --> 45:31.758
Like so good that you can
buy it at the counter.

45:31.791 --> 45:34.460
I've got a giant bottle
of the stuff back at home.

45:36.261 --> 45:37.596
Where's your family?

45:39.131 --> 45:40.399
It was just my mom,

45:42.901 --> 45:44.671
but she died.

45:44.704 --> 45:46.205
The last thing that
she said to me

45:46.238 --> 45:48.842
was to get out of Africa.

45:48.874 --> 45:53.579
And I love my people.
I do. I love my culture.

45:53.612 --> 45:56.081
It's just that it's complicated
over there,

45:56.850 --> 45:57.950
dangerous.

46:01.086 --> 46:02.488
And here it was better?

46:03.989 --> 46:05.190
I don't know.

46:06.291 --> 46:08.862
I had that, the American dream.

46:09.962 --> 46:12.331
We all dream it,

46:12.364 --> 46:16.636
but I thought that
I could actually do it.

46:18.070 --> 46:19.672
Make it a reality.

46:22.608 --> 46:24.943
It's pretty fucking stupid,
