52:01.446 --> 52:04.751
Stand right there.
I'm calling the police.

52:04.784 --> 52:07.220
Hey. Hey, don't move.

52:13.391 --> 52:15.695
Look, I'm gonna call the cops and
we're gonna get you an ambulance.

52:15.728 --> 52:17.063
We're going to
get you some help.

52:46.659 --> 52:49.327
- Kellin.
- You're Anthony's guy?

52:50.263 --> 52:51.329
Call me Johnathan.

52:55.600 --> 52:57.637
Needle, thread, antiseptic.

52:57.670 --> 52:58.971
Get yourself patched up.

52:59.005 --> 53:00.472
Take me to where you lost her.

53:01.941 --> 53:03.176
Actually, I'll follow you.

53:03.209 --> 53:04.844
