we got two problems.

55:35.593 --> 55:37.730
And I'm not having
this conversation again

55:37.763 --> 55:39.031
when we find the girl.

55:50.042 --> 55:51.711
Well, folks, we're going to
get out of your hair.

55:53.079 --> 55:55.114
No wait, wait, wait!

55:55.147 --> 55:57.515
No, no, no!

56:01.486 --> 56:03.689
So where do we go now?
Do we go back to my place.

56:03.723 --> 56:05.424
We can't. They'll track us.

56:05.458 --> 56:07.159
Your name is all over
that leasing office.

56:07.193 --> 56:09.161
Right, because I'm
trying to sell it.

56:09.195 --> 56:11.297
Look, they're going to
go to your house,

56:11.330 --> 56:13.165
and then they're gonna
go to your families.

56:13.598 --> 56:15.001
Whoa, what?

56:15.034 --> 56:16.836
What do you mean, my families?

56:16.869 --> 56:18.204
It's what they do.

56:19.405 --> 56:22.842
- What, who are you calling?
- My mom.

56:22.875 --> 56:25.077
<i>Hi, this is Carolina.
I'm sorry I missed you.</i>

56:25.111 --> 56:26.245
<i>I'll get right back to you.</i>

56:26.278 --> 56:27.480
Hey, Mom. It's Alex.

56:27.512 --> 56:28.914
Um, I'm coming to your house
right now.

56:28.948 --> 56:30.383
I just need you to
meet me there. Okay?

56:30.416 --> 56:32.617
Alright. Love you. Call me
when you get the message.

56:32.651 --> 56:33.786
Bye.

56:36.222 --> 56:37.990
All right. New plan. We're going
to my mom's house

56:38.024 --> 56:39.425
and I'm going to take her
to a hotel.

56:40.026 --> 56:41.360
What about me?

56:42.328 --> 56:43.963
You can just take my car.

56:43.996 --> 56:45.097
Okay?

56:45.131 --> 56:46.298
Just take my car,

56:46.332 --> 56:48.934
and then I'll report it stolen
