56:48.968 --> 56:50.870
And you have exactly
that amount of time

56:50.903 --> 56:52.705
to get your money
and then get out of LA

56:52.738 --> 56:55.374
and that's it. Alright?
That's all I can do for you.

56:58.744 --> 57:00.112
I'm sorry.

57:01.313 --> 57:03.182
I didn't want for
any of this to happen.

57:08.354 --> 57:10.856
Absolutely not.
Are you crazy?

57:10.890 --> 57:12.792
