57:12.825 --> 57:15.127
I'm sorry, honey. It's Tuesday.
In the middle of the week.

57:15.161 --> 57:16.796
I'm not going to
some hotel with you.

57:16.829 --> 57:18.230
It would be like a Mom-son date.

57:18.264 --> 57:20.132
You know, we could have some
strong cocktails by the pool.

57:20.766 --> 57:22.068
Are you high?

57:22.101 --> 57:24.136
We could do that too.
Whatever you want.

57:24.170 --> 57:25.704
Don't you have work?

57:25.738 --> 57:28.808
Um, no, I had an issue at
the property come up.

57:31.811 --> 57:33.546
And you? What's your deal?

57:34.246 --> 57:35.613
Are you hungry?

57:39.351 --> 57:40.953
Actually. Yeah, I am.

57:40.986 --> 57:42.655
Why don't I make you
something to eat?

57:42.688 --> 57:43.689
Thank you.

57:43.722 --> 57:45.590
Um, can I ask a question?

57:47.493 --> 57:50.296
- Who is he?
- It's my dad.

57:50.329 --> 57:52.398
It's Thomas.
He passed away a few years ago.

57:53.999 --> 57:55.267
I'm sorry.

57:56.802 --> 57:59.738
He... He's in, in your...

57:59.772 --> 58:01.173
What're you trying to say?

58:02.041 --> 58:04.176
Alex, don't be a dick.

58:04.210 --> 58:05.511
Thomas and I are both Cuban.

58:05.544 --> 58:07.346
We adopted Alex
when he was a baby.

